an american crime is a 2007 american crime drama film starring ellen page and catherine keener . the film is based on the true story of the torture and murder of sylvia &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; by indianapolis housewife gertrude &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it premiered at the 2007 sundance film festival . because of internal problems with the film 's original distributor , first look international , the film was not released theatrically . the showtime television network officially premiered an american crime on may 10 , 2008 . the film was nominated for a golden globe , a primetime emmy ( both for keener 's performance ) , and a writers guild of america award .